<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>About StoreJS</title>
    <style>
      body { background: #0d1117; color: #c9d1d9; font-family: monospace; max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
      pre { color: #58a6ff; font-size: 10px; line-height: 1.1; }
      h2 { color: #f0883e; }
      a { color: #58a6ff; }
      .stats { background: #161b22; padding: 16px; border-radius: 8px; border: 1px solid #30363d; margin: 16px 0; }
      .stats span { color: #f0883e; font-weight: bold; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <pre>
   _____ _                    _ _____ 
  / ____| |                  | / ____|
 | (___ | |_ ___  _ __ ___  | | (___  
  \___ \| __/ _ \| '__/ _ \ | |\___ \ 
  ____) | || (_) | | |  __/_| |____) |
 |_____/ \__\___/|_|  \___(_)_|_____/ 
    </pre>

    <h2>🐶 About</h2>
    <p>A demo puppy store app built for testing preview environments with SuperPlane. 🐾</p>

    <img src="https://placedog.net/300/200" alt="A random puppy" style="display:block; max-width: 300px; height: auto; border-radius: 8px; border: 1px solid #30363d; margin: 16px 0;" />

    <div class="stats">
      <p>🏗️ Runtime: <span>Node.js</span></p>
      <p>📦 Framework: <span>Express</span></p>
      <p>🛩️ Deployed via: <span>SuperPlane</span></p>
      <p>🐕 Mascot: <span>Puppies</span></p>
      <p>⏱️ Server time: <span><%= new Date().toISOString() %></span></p>
    </div>

    <p><a href="/puppies">← Back to Puppies 🐶</a></p>
  </body>
</html>

<style>
  @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
    body { background-color: #1a1a2e; color: #eaeaea; }
    a { color: #64b5f6; }
    .card { background-color: #16213e; border-color: #0f3460; }
  }
</style>
